# UnoDOS/AppleII milestone-3 round trip: open every new app, drive a key or
# two, screenshot each (HANDOFF-M3 SS7). Detailed per-app regressions live in
# tests/m3_<app>.script; this is the all-in-one smoke test.
# Run: ./build.sh test && python3 harness.py build/unodos_apple2_test.dsk shots < tests/m3.script
#
# Boot leaves the cursor on the Clock icon (index 1). Each app is reached by
# stepping the selection right, opening it (Return), then Esc back to the
# desktop. NOTE: a `wait` always separates an action key from the following
# Esc - the app's redraw must finish before Esc is polled, or the close is
# lost and the whole sequence drifts.
wait 600
# --- Theme (icon 3) ---
key right
key right
key return            # open Theme
wait 200
shot m3_all_theme
key esc
wait 24
# --- Dostris (icon 4) ---
key right
key return
wait 200
key space             # hard drop
wait 20
shot m3_all_dostris
key esc
wait 24
# --- Pac-Man (icon 5) ---
key right
key return
wait 200
shot m3_all_pacman
key esc
wait 24
# --- Music (icon 6) ---
key right
key return
wait 200
shot m3_all_music
key esc
wait 24
# --- Tracker (icon 7) ---
key right
key return
wait 200
shot m3_all_tracker
key esc
wait 24
# --- Paint (icon 8) ---
key right
key return
wait 200
shot m3_all_paint
key esc
wait 32
# --- OutLast (icon 9) ---
key right
key return
wait 200
shot m3_all_outlast
key esc
wait 24
shot m3_all_desktop   # back to the 3-row desktop
quit
